2edb15c2b994a1bdc5260f265","tid":183503,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:56:04.000Z","msg":"撐落去既意義在於每一日都覺得自己過左一關 有所得著同成長<br />\n<br />\n如果每日根本不外如是 一D新既體會領悟進步都冇<br />\n<br />\n咁捱又有乜意思呢"},{"pid":"5034e34c8be8acc3b85b3d75752d4d7106faa790","tid":183503,"uid":93287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/02/225833_797bd2b64d7e902c2dece8bf12f25c3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F02%2F225833_797bd2b64d7e902c2dece8bf12f25c3b.jpg&h=a19f7dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d94d06721ed975ed5455f5d8926c798e610588","tid":183503,"uid":87528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:00:15.000Z","msg":"明天會更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7ffabd353478a438aea0b55098c7c7cbbfc7d8","tid":183503,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:01:16.000Z","msg":"究竟我死頂到DSE有咩意義<br />\n<br />\n點解人生去到第十幾年我就輸左<br />\n<br />\n去到第二十年輸盡"},{"pid":"ee752627cf1ba928d609d06a8dec20e0e79539e6","tid":183503,"uid":84021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:02:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>It's another day of sun<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd54ccc72df13c6be0832126699a54f4b68a18ff","tid":183503,"uid":73426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:33:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟我死頂到DSE有咩意義<br />\n<br />\n點解人生去到第十幾年我就輸左<br />\n<br />\n去到第二十年輸盡</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n過多十幾廿年你回頭睇<br />\nDSE其實